div.h2: US Core NDC to CVX Code Mapping (http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/ConceptMap/ndc-cvx)
div.p: ACTIVE. Published on Jun 6, 2016 12:00:00 AM by HL7 US Realm Steering Committee.
Unit of Use NDC code mapping to the CVX Vaccine codes. Note: source = NDC and target = CVX

name.value: US Core NDC to CVX Code Mapping

description.value: Unit of Use [NDC code] (https://www2a.cdc.gov/vaccines/iis/iisstandards/ndc_crosswalk.asp) mapping to the [CVX Vaccine codes](https://www2a.cdc.gov/vaccines/iis/iisstandards/vaccines.asp?rpt=cvx). Note: source = NDC and target = CVX

purpose.value: Based upon the 2015 Edition Certification Requirements, the NDC vaccine codes SHOULD be supported as translations to the CVX vaccine codes.
